reviewText:
I totally love this show, didn't catch all the episodes on mtv, so nice to see them all at once.

Can't wait until all the other seasons are available.

I prefer this to Snoop's Fatherhood, which is 'staged/rehearsed' whatever you want to call it.

This is the original and in my opinion the best hip-hop'reality' show.

Easy to watch and just fun....

Pretty damn funny, they seem like a very close family.  I died laughing when Russy was embarrassed that his dad was picking him up from the Bus Stop in a $250,000 Phantom. So Run shows up the next day in the same ride wearing a Gorilla Suit.  And watching Russy destroy his game boys never gets old.  This is one of the best reality shows I've seen. And Run hiding his wifes burgers from Wendy's because he wanted her to go on a diet, and her spending half the episode looking for them LOL.
This a great spiritual family. Although at times the kids are a little bratty!  Great Show!!!!!!!!
My brother absolutely loves his new videos!!!  He is looking for season 3 already!!!
Who doesn't love rev run and the family! They're such a cute and hilarious group! =o]
I watched this show a lot while it was still new and now I'm going through it again watching it with my roommate who has never seen it.  We love it!
I'm happy with my purchase
I miss this show so much.  Really wish they would actually produce a box set of the final seasons.  This is what reality tv SHOULD be!!!
I love it!

this is a great item it has 3 disc a good show to watch even when it came on mtv and another channel as well, great item for family's who love run dmc and rev runs quotes and sayings  also this deals with family crises and other stuff love this item.
I love Run's house. I love the Rev. Run is all about family.
Just like old days very nice:)
I miss this show
A funny family that is thoroughly entertaining in this reality show.
The show is good but I think a pastor should behave like a pastor and so should his kids. Love his wife's naturally sweet spirit.
Love this show! :) Funny, family oriented, and clean:)
I used to watch Run's House like everyday of my life. I loved the family interaction. I can tell that Rev. Run really loves his family. Comedy mixed with real parenting. Way to go Run.
I remember watching this show on MTV when it first came on.  Not a bad show if I say so myself.  You know what's funny? Diggy became the "big" rapper in the family but not JoJo? Hm.
I love the way Rev. Run raise his children and make them work for everything they get. Such a grounded way of living.
Run's House! I really hate that this isn't on TV anymore. It's nice to see an African American family on a reality show, and they aren't ghetto. I really miss this show!

What a joy to watch I remember I use to watch ruin's house each week I could not wait for the next episode! These people are beautiful and so wise with their money. May God continue to bless them abundantly!
going to have to get more seasons was what i was looking for and got here on time and good product
Just an amazing item and would recommend this to anyone and the service was great as can be!  Just awesome!

Great collection of DVDs from one of the nicer reality tv shows in history. This family reminds me of a mixture of the Cosby Show, with a Hip Hop flavor.  Each segment ends on a positive note. Rev Run is the head of household and his kids are typical teens and pre-teens. Very funny and family-friendly.

I purchase a dvd set from this company,it was damage i flied a complaint but they told me if i drop the complaint they would handle the problem and that was a lie i was out of a dvd and out of my money.i would never purchase nothing from this coming and i hope this help the next person.
Husbands favorite
Good family show.
I love Run's House I couldn't find it anywhere else

I honestly thought that the tv show was gonna be a lot more mega after reading the details on the site before purchasing but I was disappointed.
I can say that Rev Run is definitely a family man and loves his family. He also teaches values.
Very entertaining and prompt delivery
I love Run's House great show. I  give it 5 stars.
I like it so much nice dvd
Good buy. Great show.
DVD arrived on time and work just fine.
classic!! enough said
